'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #2940] on 2 November 2000 at 6:20:24 pm'!"Change Set:		fasterPNGDate:			2 November 2000Author:			Bob Arning- speed up deoding of some PNG images by reducing the amount of large integer math"!!PNGReadWriter methodsFor: 'pixel copies' stamp: 'RAA 11/2/2000 18:19'!copyPixelsRGB: y	"Handle non-interlaced RGB color mode (colorType = 2)"	| i pixel b |	b _ BitBlt current bitPokerToForm: form.	bitsPerChannel = 8		ifTrue: [			0 to: width-1 do: [ :x |				i _ (x * 3) + 1.				pixel _ ((thisScanline at: i)<<16)					+ ((thisScanline at: i+1)<<8)					+ ((thisScanline at: i+2)).				b pixelAt: x@y put: 16rFF000000 + pixel.				]			]		ifFalse: [			0 to: width-1 do: [ :x |				i _ (x * 6) + 1.				pixel _ ((thisScanline at: i)<<16)					+ ((thisScanline at: i+2)<<8)					+ ((thisScanline at: i+4)).				b pixelAt: x@y put: 16rFF000000 + pixel.				]			]! !